      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in absolute showroom condition. This specimen boasts a flawless aesthetic profile and a meticulously preserved interior, reflecting an uncompromising standard of previous ownership. Every mechanical and cosmetic detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the expectations of the most discerning buyer. This is a rare opportunity to secure a vehicle of peerless quality and distinction.",
