    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is a total stunner. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered and garage-kept its whole life, so everything is looking totally flawless. If you\u2019ve been searching for a ride that's basically brand new without the brand new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. I'd love for you to come by, say hi, and see it for yourself!",
      "price": 43500.0,
