    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies. This example is mechanically pristine, boasting a documented VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox offers crisp engagement, paired with a perfectly functioning variable M differential lock. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, providing the telepathic handling these chassis are known for. Finished in original paint with an interior free of bolster wear or pixel degradation, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-division engineering. Turn-key and ready for the most rigorous PPI.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
