    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since the day it left the dealership. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no swirl marks or stone chips, while the interior remains pristine, featuring supple leather seats with no bolster wear and original factory floor mats. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been strictly maintained with a full service history and stored in a climate-controlled garage. For the buyer seeking an investment-grade example that drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 46500.0,
